==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: The face of a peach blossom.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: rén miàn táo huā

===Idiom===
'''[[人]][[面]][[桃花]]'''

# Describes a man's nostalgic memory of an old sweetheart.

===Noun===
# Name of a [[wikipedia:Peking_opera|Peking opera]] play.

